parameters.text:
Create a professional order confirmation email for this order:

Product: {{ $json.product.name }}
Brand: {{ $json.product.brand }}
SKU: {{ $json.product.sku }}
Category: {{ $json.product.category }}
Variant: {{ $json.variant.size }}
Price per Case: ${{ $json.variant.price }}
Units per Case: {{ $json.variant.caseQty }}
Quantity: {{ $json.quantity }} cases
Total: ${{ $json.totalPrice }}
Customer Email: {{ $json.email }}
Order Date: {{ $json.orderDate }}

Create a friendly, professional confirmation that:
1. Thanks them for their order
2. Lists order details clearly
3. Shows total price prominently
4. Mentions 1-2 business day processing time
5. Includes contact email: orders@salmocatalog.com

Format as clean HTML for email with inline styles. Use a professional color scheme.
